  <h>bi</h>
  <p><g>bi</g>
    <en>be</en> is the predicative verb</p>
  <section id="forms">
    <h>forms</h>
    <p>The principal parts of <g>bi</g> are – <ul>
        <li><m>bidh</m> – future independent <en>will be</en>
        </li>
        <li><m>bha</m> – past independent <en>was</en>
        </li>
        <li><m>bhiodh</m> – conditional independent <en>would be</en>
        </li>
        <li><m>bith</m> – verbal noun <en>being</en>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <section>
      <h>tense</h>
      <p><ul>
          <li>present <ul id="present">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>tha</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>tha</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>eil</m>, a <m>bheil</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>thathar</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>thathar</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>eilear</m>, a <m>bheilear</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>past <ul id="past">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>bha</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>bha</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>robh</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>bhathar</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>bhathar</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>robhar</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>future <ul id="future">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>bidh</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>bhios</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha <m>bhi</m>, am/nach <m>bi</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>bithear</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>bhithear</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha <m>bhithear</m>, am/nach <m>bithear</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>conditional <ul id="conditional">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>first person singular <ul>
                      <li>independent – <m>bhithinn</m></li>
                      <li>relative – a <m>bhithinn</m></li>
                      <li>dependent – cha <m>bhithinn</m>, am/nach <m>bithinn</m></li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                  <li>first person plural <ul>
                      <li>independent – <m>bhiomaid</m></li>
                      <li>relative – a <m>bhiomaid</m></li>
                      <li>dependent – cha <m>bhiomaid</m>, am/nach <m>biomaid</m></li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                  <li>second/third persons <ul>
                      <li>independent – <m>bhiodh</m></li>
                      <li>relative – a <m>bhiodh</m></li>
                      <li>dependent – cha <m>bhiodh</m>, am/nach <m>bhiodh</m></li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>bhite</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>bhite</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – cha <m>bhite</m>, am/nach <m>bite</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul></p>
    </section>
